<div id="hotspotminingContent-423323" class="hotspotminingContent clearfix showPic" style="display: block">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_pic ">
<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=4c205afcd1861034abb511f2&lemmaId=22587&lemmaId=22587&fr=qingtian" target="_blank"><img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/whfpf%3D360%2C280%2C50/sign=52433f708413632715b89173f7b293da/7a899e510fb30f24013b4fafc695d143ac4b03fc.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=4c205afcd1861034abb511f2&lemmaId=22587&lemmaId=22587&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">历史上真实的唐伯虎到底是什么样？</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2019-05-28 21:05</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>唐寅于明成化六年出生于苏州，父亲唐广德，靠做小生意养活一家五口人的生活。少年唐寅记忆力超群，过目成诵，读书速度奇快，“每夜尽一卷”。唐广德认识到儿子超凡的天资，不惜重金延请名师教导唐寅，几年之后便超过了老师。唐寅在人物、山水、花鸟等多种题材上都有很高的造诣。</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=4c205afcd1861034abb511f2&lemmaId=22587&lemmaId=22587&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
</div>
