</div>
<div id="hotspotminingContent-316548" class="hotspotminingContent clearfix showPic" >
<div class="hotspotminingContent_pic ">
<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=5d5bb1f89881f3495d7b211f&fr=qingtian&lemmaId=22587" target="_blank"><img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/whfpf%3D360%2C280%2C50/sign=abb8d628c71349547e4bbb243073a16e/37d3d539b6003af3cfe0b2c9392ac65c1138b6c5.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=5d5bb1f89881f3495d7b211f&fr=qingtian&lemmaId=22587" target="_blank">明朝史上最悲剧的文人，风流才子不风流，官场失意情场更惨</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2018-05-21 20:05</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>​说起历史上命运最悲惨的文人，那就非唐伯虎莫属了。如果你真的了解他的一生的话，就会认为此言非虚。提起唐伯虎，我们肯定会不假思索地想到两个关键词：江南四大才子，秋香。</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=5d5bb1f89881f3495d7b211f&fr=qingtian&lemmaId=22587" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
