<div class="para" label-module="para">《枯槎鸜鹆图》</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="4_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub6825980_4_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="书法" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="4-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">唐寅</span>书法</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">《古诗二十七首》<a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" title="唐寅书法"  href="/pic/%E5%94%90%E5%AF%85/22587/18394261/3b292df5e0fe9925adf4def632a85edf8cb1719f?fr=lemma&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:146px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:144px;height:220px;">
