<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="5d5bb1f89881f3495d7b211f">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=5631369c&authorId=b3e54008a24ed52773648f25&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/08f790529822720e58ce082377cb0a46f31fabe3.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>历史大学堂</strong>
<span>品读书史，历史堂原创出品</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=5d5bb1f89881f3495d7b211f&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/95eef01f3a292df594d38ebcb0315c6034a87302.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
明朝史上最悲剧的文人，风流才子不风流，官场失意情场更惨
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=5d5bb1f89881f3495d7b211f&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
​说起历史上命运最悲惨的文人，那就非唐伯虎莫属了。如果你真的了解他的一生的话，就会认为此言非虚。提起唐伯虎，我们肯定会不假思索地想到两个关键词：江南四大才子，秋香。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-05-21</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">436</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="a2db9e0a9ff3abf4eeb777fb">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=150736a3&authorId=d986c0a0c04379765d687821&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/d439b6003af33a876e6dfd81c85c10385343b52d.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>在下刀掌门</strong>
<span>历史评论学者社群</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=a2db9e0a9ff3abf4eeb777fb&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b64543a98226cffc6d8708aab2014a90f603ea7d.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
真实的唐伯虎确实惨绝人寰，几次自杀未遂
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=a2db9e0a9ff3abf4eeb777fb&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
“花坞里桃花庵，桃花庵下桃花仙;桃花仙人种桃树，又摘桃花换酒钱。酒醒只在花前坐，酒醉还来花下眠;半醒半醉日复日，花落花开年复年。但愿老死花酒间，不愿鞠躬车马前;车尘马足富者趣，酒盏花枝贫者缘。若将富贵比贫者，一在平地一在天;若将贫贱比车马，他得驱驰我得闲。别人笑我太疯癫，我...</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-09-21</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">411</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="76f8efb94081c8cf8efed665">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=76f8efb94081c8cf8efed665&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/8d5494eef01f3a296f69a6bb9725bc315c607c25.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
江南才子唐伯虎与《红楼梦》有着哪些隐秘的联系？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=76f8efb94081c8cf8efed665&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
记得俞平伯1923年出版《红楼梦辨》，在附录中收了《唐六如与林黛玉》一文，一开头就说：“读者看了这个标题，想没有一个不要笑的，以为我大约是在那边大发精神病了。”其实，这篇文章并不是为了讨笑，而是讨论《红楼梦》中黛玉葬花这个情节。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-04-02</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">312</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="7a442b4091140ec8e1b3fb73">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=fa0307ae&authorId=2767bec0450c7bac71673620&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/2f738bd4b31c870113cad2212b7f9e2f0608fffd.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>世界华人周刊</strong>
<span>海外观察第一站，百度百科TA说特邀科普合作方。</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=7a442b4091140ec8e1b3fb73&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b3b7d0a20cf431adebf2324c4536acaf2edd98a6.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
风流才子唐伯虎——不自律，毁一生
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=7a442b4091140ec8e1b3fb73&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
真相最后演绎成了传说，传说又进一步演化成传奇，一个个动人的故事连同那些难以述说的世俗欲望，都安放进唐伯虎的生平故事里，随着岁月的流淌，这些传奇故事在里面酝酿、发酵，弥散出诱人的酒香，最终，唐伯虎幻化为文化星空中最烂漫洒脱的一颗星星。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-04-02</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">266</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="b8afdc4418018938626eb796">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=b8afdc4418018938626eb796&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/78310a55b319ebc41fca05ec8c26cffc1e171610.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
风流才子唐伯虎的人生中发生了什么事，迫使他装疯卖傻？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=b8afdc4418018938626eb796&lemmaId=22587&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
正德年间，唐伯虎迫于生计，接受宁王朱宸濠的聘请，到宁王府任职。不久唐伯虎发现了宁王的种种谋反行为，作为一个名人，他深感在其府中难逃杀身之祸。为脱离险境他打出了这样的主意，常常披头散发，花着一张脸，穿着破烂的衣服，溜到大街上去东蹦西跳高唱低吟，惹得不少人跟随围观。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-04-02</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">235</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul></div>
