<span class="site">．凤凰网</span><span>&#91;引用日期2019-09-17&#93;</span></li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type1 " id="reference-[3]-6825980-wrap">
<span class="index">3.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_3_6825980" id="refIndex_3_6825980" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[3]_6825980">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<a rel="nofollow" href="/reference/22587/1a71_-4ngEIYviAAJnlbvjTGYUmLkr-tYaNtpqTYYkOYs7Bf3qmaLtbot2OkJtH-RdVAT2_VddNPtdt0gr07Bg" target="_blank" class="text">唐寅<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a>
<span class="site">．中国书画网</span><span>&#91;引用日期2015-08-29&#93;</span></li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type1 " id="reference-[4]-6825980-wrap">
<span class="index">4.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_4_6825980" id="refIndex_4_6825980" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[4]_6825980">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<a rel="nofollow" href="/reference/22587/889bJPmsQDnBDaFMuGvSTaeCdycHZvyDmgrzAy4MJg9kgRe8dQ7455DeqS-_kTuQnC1h-tu7-rgcrTFVBs_YFiiTROZ81pw0bRw0m2_ROnt3DEV_NtQ5NsInXMToPm8doeIHOU50ZzBV-0XdLVubgZQDf0jnUaPQupBqmSPgja9SxN6nTPkWZU-3ApbQJ2XTlT8" target="_blank" class="text">唐寅<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a>
<span class="site">．浙江图书馆中国历代名人图像细览</span><span>&#91;引用日期2018-07-27&#93;</span></li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 " id="reference-[5]-6825980-wrap">
<span class="index">5.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_5_6825980" id="refIndex_5_6825980" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[5]_6825980">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span class="text">祝允明《唐子畏墓志并铭》：唐氏世吴人，居吴趋里，子畏母丘氏，以成化六年二月初四日生子畏，岁舍庚寅，名之曰寅。</span>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type2 " id="reference-[6]-6825980-wrap">
<span class="index">6.</span>
